#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.126"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.126:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.126:0.2"
msgid "13. Kusināravagga"
msgstr "13. Kusināra"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.126:0.3"
msgid "126. Bharaṇḍukālāmasutta"
msgstr "126. Bharaṇḍu Kālāma"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.126:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno yena kapilavatthu tadavasari."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was wandering in the land of the Kosalans when he "
"arrived at Kapilavatthu."

msgctxt "an3.126:1.2"
msgid "Assosi kho mahānāmo sakko: “bhagavā kira kapilavatthuṃ anuppatto”ti."
msgstr "Mahānāma the Sakyan heard that he had arrived."

msgctxt "an3.126:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho mahānāmo sakko yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitaṃ kho mahānāmaṃ "
"sakkaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"He went up to the Buddha, bowed, and stood to one side. The Buddha said to "
"him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli1.277"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.126:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Gaccha, mahānāma, kapilavatthusmiṃ, tathārūpaṃ āvasathaṃ jāna yatthajja "
"mayaṃ ekarattiṃ vihareyyāmā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Go into Kapilavatthu, Mahānāma, and check if there’s a suitable guest house "
"where I can spend the night.”"

#. VAR: anvāhiṇḍanto → āhiṇḍanto (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an3.126:2.2"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho mahānāmo sakko bhagavato paṭissutvā kapilavatthuṃ "
"pavisitvā kevalakappaṃ kapilavatthuṃ anvāhiṇḍanto nāddasa kapilavatthusmiṃ "
"tathārūpaṃ āvasathaṃ yatthajja bhagavā ekarattiṃ vihareyya."
msgstr ""
"“Yes, sir,” replied Mahānāma. He returned to Kapilavatthu and searched all "
"over the city, but he couldn’t see a suitable guest house for the Buddha to "
"spend the night."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.126:3.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho mahānāmo sakko yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then Mahānāma went up to the Buddha, and said to him:"

msgctxt "an3.126:3.2"
msgid ""
"“natthi, bhante, kapilavatthusmiṃ tathārūpo āvasatho yatthajja bhagavā "
"ekarattiṃ vihareyya."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, there’s no suitable guest house in Kapilavatthu for you to spend the "
"night."

msgctxt "an3.126:3.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhante, bharaṇḍu kālāmo bhagavato purāṇasabrahmacārī."
msgstr ""
"But there is this Bharaṇḍu the Kālāman, who used to be the Buddha’s "
"spiritual companion."

msgctxt "an3.126:3.4"
msgid "Tassajja bhagavā assame ekarattiṃ viharatū”ti."
msgstr "Why don’t you spend the night at his hermitage?”"

msgctxt "an3.126:3.5"
msgid "“Gaccha, mahānāma, santharaṃ paññāpehī”ti."
msgstr "“Go, Mahānāma, and set out a mat.”"

msgctxt "an3.126:3.6"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho mahānāmo sakko bhagavato paṭissutvā yena bharaṇḍussa "
"kālāmassa assamo tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā santharaṃ paññāpetvā udakaṃ "
"ṭhapetvā pādānaṃ dhovanāya yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"“Yes, sir,” replied Mahānāma. He went to Bharaṇḍu’s hermitage, where he set "
"out a mat, and got foot-washing water ready. Then he went back to the Buddha "
"and said to him:"

msgctxt "an3.126:3.7"
msgid "“santhato, bhante, santhāro, udakaṃ ṭhapitaṃ pādānaṃ dhovanāya."
msgstr "“The mat and foot-washing water are set out."

msgctxt "an3.126:3.8"
msgid "Yassadāni, bhante, bhagavā kālaṃ maññatī”ti."
msgstr "Please, sir, go at your convenience.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.126:4.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā yena bharaṇḍussa kālāmassa assamo tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha went to Bharaṇḍu’s hermitage, sat down on the seat spread "
"out,"

msgctxt "an3.126:4.2"
msgid "Nisajja kho bhagavā pāde pakkhālesi."
msgstr "and washed his feet."

msgctxt "an3.126:4.3"
msgid "Atha kho mahānāmassa sakkassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then it occurred to Mahānāma:"

msgctxt "an3.126:4.4"
msgid "“akālo kho ajja bhagavantaṃ payirupāsituṃ."
msgstr "“It’s too late to pay homage to the Buddha today."

msgctxt "an3.126:4.5"
msgid "Kilanto bhagavā."
msgstr "He’s tired."

msgctxt "an3.126:4.6"
msgid ""
"Sve dānāhaṃ bhagavantaṃ payirupāsissāmī”ti bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā "
"padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi."
msgstr ""
"Tomorrow I’ll pay homage to the Buddha.” He bowed to the Buddha and "
"respectfully circled him, keeping him on his right, then he left."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli1.278"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an3.126:5.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho mahānāmo sakko tassā rattiyā accayena yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho mahānāmaṃ sakkaṃ "
"bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then, when the night had passed, Mahānāma the Sakyan went up to the Buddha, "
"and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "an3.126:5.2"
msgid "“tayo khome, mahānāma, satthāro santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "“Mahānāma, there are these three teachers found in the world."

msgctxt "an3.126:5.3"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.126:5.4"
msgid "Idha, mahānāma, ekacco satthā kāmānaṃ pariññaṃ paññāpeti;"
msgstr "One teacher advocates the complete understanding of sensual pleasures,"

msgctxt "an3.126:5.5"
msgid "na rūpānaṃ pariññaṃ paññāpeti, na vedanānaṃ pariññaṃ paññāpeti."
msgstr "but not of sights or feelings."

msgctxt "an3.126:5.6"
msgid ""
"Idha pana, mahānāma, ekacco satthā kāmānaṃ pariññaṃ paññāpeti, rūpānaṃ "
"pariññaṃ paññāpeti;"
msgstr ""
"One teacher advocates the complete understanding of sensual pleasures and "
"sights,"

msgctxt "an3.126:5.7"
msgid "na vedanānaṃ pariññaṃ paññāpeti."
msgstr "but not of feelings."

msgctxt "an3.126:5.8"
msgid ""
"Idha pana, mahānāma, ekacco satthā kāmānaṃ pariññaṃ paññāpeti, rūpānaṃ "
"pariññaṃ paññāpeti, vedanānaṃ pariññaṃ paññāpeti."
msgstr ""
"One teacher advocates the complete understanding of sensual pleasures, "
"sights, and feelings."

msgctxt "an3.126:5.9"
msgid "Ime kho, mahānāma, tayo satthāro santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "These are the three teachers found in the world."

msgctxt "an3.126:5.10"
msgid "Imesaṃ, mahānāma, tiṇṇaṃ satthārānaṃ ekā niṭṭhā udāhu puthu niṭṭhā”ti?"
msgstr "Do these three teachers have the same goal or different goals?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an3.126:6.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bharaṇḍu kālāmo mahānāmaṃ sakkaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, Bharaṇḍu said to Mahānāma:"

msgctxt "an3.126:6.2"
msgid "“ekāti, mahānāma, vadehī”ti."
msgstr "“Say they’re the same, Mahānāma!”"

msgctxt "an3.126:6.3"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bhagavā mahānāmaṃ sakkaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said:"

msgctxt "an3.126:6.4"
msgid "“nānāti, mahānāma, vadehī”ti."
msgstr "“Say they’re different, Mahānāma!”"

msgctxt "an3.126:6.5"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho bharaṇḍu kālāmo mahānāmaṃ sakkaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "For a second time, Bharaṇḍu said:"

msgctxt "an3.126:6.6"
msgid "“ekāti, mahānāma, vadehī”ti."
msgstr "“Say they’re the same, Mahānāma!”"

msgctxt "an3.126:6.7"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho bhagavā mahānāmaṃ sakkaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said:"

msgctxt "an3.126:6.8"
msgid "“nānāti, mahānāma, vadehī”ti."
msgstr "“Say they’re different, Mahānāma!”"

msgctxt "an3.126:6.9"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho bharaṇḍu kālāmo mahānāmaṃ sakkaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "For a third time, Bharaṇḍu said:"

msgctxt "an3.126:6.10"
msgid "“ekāti, mahānāma, vadehī”ti."
msgstr "“Say they’re the same, Mahānāma!”"

msgctxt "an3.126:6.11"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho bhagavā mahānāmaṃ sakkaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said:"

msgctxt "an3.126:6.12"
msgid "“nānāti, mahānāma, vadehī”ti."
msgstr "“Say they’re different, Mahānāma!”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
#. VAR: bharaṇḍu → bharaṇḍussa (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "an3.126:7.1"
msgid "Atha kho bharaṇḍu kālāmassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then it occurred to Bharaṇḍu:"

msgctxt "an3.126:7.2"
msgid ""
"“mahesakkhassa vatamhi mahānāmassa sakkassa sammukhā samaṇena gotamena "
"yāvatatiyaṃ apasādito."
msgstr ""
"“The Buddha has rebuked me three times in front of this illustrious Mahānāma."

msgctxt "an3.126:7.3"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ kapilavatthumhā pakkameyyan”ti."
msgstr "Why don’t I leave Kapilavatthu?”"

msgctxt "an3.126:7.4"
msgid "Atha kho bharaṇḍu kālāmo kapilavatthumhā pakkāmi."
msgstr "Then Bharaṇḍu the Kālāman left Kapilavatthu,"

msgctxt "an3.126:7.5"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ kapilavatthumhā pakkāmi tathā pakkantova ahosi na puna paccāgacchīti."
msgstr "never to return."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.126:7.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
